They killed sixteen Mexicans, scalping them and burning their bodies with the wagons.

abstract: ATTEMPTED SUICIDE.--At 8:30 o'clock yesterday afternoon, a German, named HENRY BODER, 86 years of age, residing at No. 14 Leonard-street, attempted to commit suicide by hanging himself in his room. It was supposed that he was insane, and he was therefore taken to the Fifth Precinct Station-house and locked up.
